\s Mufananidzo wedzimba mbiri
\p
\v 24 Naizvozvo mumwe nomumwe unonzwa mashoko angu awa, akaaita, ndichamufananidza nomurume wakachenjera, wakavaka imba yake paruware.
\v 25 Mvura ikaturuka, mafashame akauya, mitutu ikavhuvhuta, ikarova paimba iyo, ikasawa; nokuti yakanga yakateyiwa paruware.
\v 26 Zvino mumwe nomumwe unonzwa mashoko angu awa, akasaaita, uchafananidzwa nomurume benzi, wakavaka imba yake pajecha;
\v 27 mvura ikaturuka, mafashame akauya, mitutu ikavhuvhuta, ikarova imba iyo, ikawa, kuwa kwayo kukava kukuru.
\p
\v 28 Zvino zvakaitika kuti Jesu apedza mashoko iwawa, zvaunga zvakashamiswa nedzidziso yake.
\v 29 Nokuti wakavadzidzisa soune simba, kwete savanyori.
